    <div id="topics">
        <div class="post">
            <h1 class = "postTitle">
                
<a id="cb_post_title_url" class="postTitle2 vertical-middle" href="https://www.cnblogs.com/zhonglongbo/p/13876563.html">
    <span>拿了十几个offer，怎样做选择？</span>
    


</a>

            </h1>
            <div class="clear"></div>
            <div class="postBody">
                
    <div id="cnblogs_post_description" style="display: none">
        幸福的烦恼来的太突然，一下把我砸的晕头转向.....
    </div>
<div id="cnblogs_post_body" class="blogpost-body cnblogs-markdown">
    <div class="output_wrapper" id="output_wrapper_id" style="font-size: 15px; color: rgba(62, 62, 62, 1); line-height: 1.8; word-spacing: 2px; letter-spacing: 2px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(50, 0, 0, 0.05) 3%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 3%), linear-gradient(360deg, rgba(50, 0, 0, 0.05) 3%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 3%); background-size: 20px 20px; background-position: center"><p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">本文已经收录至我的GitHub,欢迎大家踊跃star 和 issues。</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">https://github.com/midou-tech/articles</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">最近收到好几个读者的咨询，关于如何选offer的问题，暖心的龙叔都一一解答了</p>
<figure style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0"><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/007S8ZIlly1gjw5x11lxbj30t0078gmx.jpg" alt="" title="" style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; display: block; margin: 0 auto; max-width: 100%"><figcaption style="line-height: inherit; margin: 10px 0 0; padding: 0; text-align: center; color: rgba(153, 153, 153, 1); font-size: 0.7em"></figcaption></figure>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">大家问的问题，忽然又唤起了我的回忆</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">那个秋天很特别，马上秋招了，出了点车祸，休息了大概一个月，一直晚到9.6号才入场秋招，入场时我的嘴还是封着线</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">那段时间还爱上了杨超越，以为这是一场持久战，必须给自己一点精神食粮，准备好了一切去迎接生活的馈赠</p>
<figure style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0"><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/007S8ZIlly1gjs643p326j30h80biaf2.jpg" alt="" title="" style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; display: block; margin: 0 auto; max-width: 100%"><figcaption style="line-height: inherit; margin: 10px 0 0; padding: 0; text-align: center; color: rgba(153, 153, 153, 1); font-size: 0.7em"></figcaption></figure>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">然而事实告诉我，真正的猛男总是能 <strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">速战速决</strong>，从国庆开始秋招基本结束，就进入了下一段旅途——毕业生活</p>
<figure style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0"><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/007S8ZIlly1gjs63d09m3j30hs0fa7bd.jpg" alt="" title="" style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; display: block; margin: 0 auto; max-width: 100%"><figcaption style="line-height: inherit; margin: 10px 0 0; padding: 0; text-align: center; color: rgba(153, 153, 153, 1); font-size: 0.7em"></figcaption></figure>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">但是好景不长，蜂拥而至的offer砸向了我，那一刻我眼花缭乱，被砸晕了</p>
<figure style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0"><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/007S8ZIlly1gjs6vvbns8j30hk0e640q.jpg" alt="" title="" style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; display: block; margin: 0 auto; max-width: 100%"><figcaption style="line-height: inherit; margin: 10px 0 0; padding: 0; text-align: center; color: rgba(153, 153, 153, 1); font-size: 0.7em"></figcaption></figure>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">和大家一样，我也陷入了对人生，对未来的思考</p>
<figure style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0"><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/007S8ZIlly1gjs7n36ks0g308c08cmx4.gif" alt="" title="" style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; display: block; margin: 0 auto; max-width: 100%"><figcaption style="line-height: inherit; margin: 10px 0 0; padding: 0; text-align: center; color: rgba(153, 153, 153, 1); font-size: 0.7em"></figcaption></figure>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">秋天的风不再缠绵，而是有些微醺，我必须时刻保持清醒</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">那段时间，同学之间见面打招呼，一定是这样子</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">同学A：班长签哪里了？</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">龙叔：还没定…</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">同学B：签哪里了？</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">龙叔：还没定…</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">也不能老是犹豫不决，最坏的选择就是拖着不选择</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">于是我把这些offer都罗列了一遍，把我要选择的点做了一个优先级排序，从左往右优先级依次降低</p>
<figure style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0"><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/007S8ZIlly1gjs81hdr3kj31940u0akw.jpg" alt="" title="" style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; display: block; margin: 0 auto; max-width: 100%"><figcaption style="line-height: inherit; margin: 10px 0 0; padding: 0; text-align: center; color: rgba(153, 153, 153, 1); font-size: 0.7em"></figcaption></figure>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">接下来龙叔从六个方向说说，如何把自己卖个好价钱✌️</p>
<h3 id="h" style="color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.6em 0; font-weight: bold; border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(239, 112, 96, 1); font-size: 1.3em"><span style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0 3px 0 0; display: inline-block; font-weight: normal; background: rgba(239, 112, 96, 1); color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1); padding: 3px 10px 1px; border-top-right-radius: 3px; border-top-left-radius: 3px">城市选择</span><span style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-bottom: 36px solid rgba(239, 235, 233, 1); border-right: 20px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)"> </span></h3>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">城市选择很重要，一个城市的选择代表着你选择了一个环境，代表着你未来的生活水准，代表你能走多远</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">选择城市，可不是简单的考虑是否离家近，是否和对象一个城市</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">这些因素需要考虑，但<strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">切忌</strong>作为首要考虑城市的因素</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">举个我的老友A例子，毕业找工作时下定决心要去女朋友的城市，而且选择<strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">面哪家公司</strong>都是看女朋友有么有参加</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">最终放弃了一家 <strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">行业地位高</strong>、<strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">公司技术底蕴好</strong>、<strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">给的岗位也非常nice</strong>、领导<strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">多次沟通</strong>想要他去 的公司，最后<strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">随便</strong>选择了一家女友城市的公司</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">简单来说就是放弃了一家<strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">什么都好</strong>就是女朋友不在的的城市，选择了一个<strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">什么都不好</strong>，只有女朋友在的城市</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">他以为从此拥有了世界，殊不知世界早已抛弃他</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">女友选择自己非常喜欢的<strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">公司</strong>和<strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">岗位</strong></p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">毕业后在公司做的非常出色，老板很器重她，自己能力也得到很大提升，很快升职加薪</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">每次回到家和男友都是小心翼翼的说话，生怕一个不小心就是伤害</p>
<figure style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0"><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/007S8ZIlly1gjw65a7n8xj307z06bq2y.jpg" alt="" title="" style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; display: block; margin: 0 auto; max-width: 100%"><figcaption style="line-height: inherit; margin: 10px 0 0; padding: 0; text-align: center; color: rgba(153, 153, 153, 1); font-size: 0.7em"></figcaption></figure>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">而那个男孩子，岗位不是他喜欢的，工作没动力；公司是个创业公司，薪资低偶尔发不出来工资；老板整天想着怎么让公司活下来，对员工也是最大化压榨，经常性加班到很晚</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">社会的毒打让他失去了对<strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">生活热爱</strong>，对待感情也没有了当初的<strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">耐心和执着</strong>，对未来增加了更多的<strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">迷茫</strong></p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">工作在占据了一大半的生活，如果工作一点兴奋都没有，我真的想象不到你的生活会有怎样的开心</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">事业是自己的，感情是不确定的，人的感情会根据现实情况发生很多变化的</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">也许当初听了我们的一丁点劝阻，也许…</p>
<figure style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0"><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/007S8ZIlly1gjw6q20yrag306y06y761.gif" alt="" title="" style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; display: block; margin: 0 auto; max-width: 100%"><figcaption style="line-height: inherit; margin: 10px 0 0; padding: 0; text-align: center; color: rgba(153, 153, 153, 1); font-size: 0.7em"></figcaption></figure>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">所以我们在选择城市首先要考虑的是以下几点：</p>
<ul style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0 0 0 32px; list-style-type: disc">
<li style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0 0 0.5em; padding: 0"><span style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0">行业密集型</span></li>
<li style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0 0 0.5em; padding: 0"><span style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0">高速发展、人口密集</span></li>
<li style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0 0 0.5em; padding: 0"><span style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0">行业底蕴深厚</span></li>
</ul>
<h4 id="h-1" style="color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.6em 0; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.2em"><span style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0">行业密集型</span></h4>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">一个行业密集型的城市，意味着<strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">机会比边缘城市多很多</strong>，行业密集型时，政府、人才、资本家都会向这里倾斜</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">行业上下游链条完整，很容易接触到行业的<strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">上下游</strong>，对职业成长帮助很大。</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">行业密集，资源竞争激烈，对人才的竞争也会很激烈，你的价值会得到更充分的体现。</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">像我虽然没那么强，但是经常收到各种猎头的电话挖角（真的痛恨那个恶心人泄露我的电话），被迫无奈最后把手机号直接换了。</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">溢价概率更高，对人才渴求度了，自然就有人被迫溢价了。</p>
<h4 id="h-2" style="color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.6em 0; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.2em"><span style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0">高速发展、人口密集</span></h4>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">在短视频发展的如今，小城市里的你感觉和大城市的信息差没那么大了，其实不然</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">信息差在任何发达的社会都会存在，因为有一个很重要的因素，社会具有群体效应，有圈子的存在。</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">小城市可能节奏慢、圈子固定，很容易让你陷入一种舒适区</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">而在高速发展、人口密集的大城市，人们的文化程度、受教育程度、信息发散程度、圈子间碰撞和流动性都会增多。</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">而这些因素都会使你的价值观、职业发展、人生走向产生很大的变化</p>
<h3 id="h-3" style="color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.6em 0; font-weight: bold; border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(239, 112, 96, 1); font-size: 1.3em"><span style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0 3px 0 0; display: inline-block; font-weight: normal; background: rgba(239, 112, 96, 1); color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1); padding: 3px 10px 1px; border-top-right-radius: 3px; border-top-left-radius: 3px">公司&amp;产品</span><span style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-bottom: 36px solid rgba(239, 235, 233, 1); border-right: 20px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)"> </span></h3>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">好的公司和靠谱的产品</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">刚找工作那会大家对公司了解程度太浅，记得我毕业面试那会，非常流行东南亚杀猪盘。</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">招你过去，保安持枪上班，写完bug就是一顿爆锤，让你天天菊花残，这种例子网上很多。</p>
<figure style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0"><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/007S8ZIlly1gjv1hkdqkjj30u00rfgnd.jpg" alt="" title="" style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; display: block; margin: 0 auto; max-width: 100%"><figcaption style="line-height: inherit; margin: 10px 0 0; padding: 0; text-align: center; color: rgba(153, 153, 153, 1); font-size: 0.7em"></figcaption></figure>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">这种公司很好识别，网上一搜 总部在国外，国内无办地点，只存在一些招聘人员或者挂着一些莫须有的公司名字。</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">一般灰产行业的公司承诺的<strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">薪资待遇</strong>都非常优厚，其他条件也给你承诺的<strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">非常完美</strong>，但是等你一入职就两眼一抹黑，被限制人生自由。</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">完美本身就是一种不完美，所以只要你稍微警惕一点也就不至于。</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">对于不了解的公司多在网上查询资料，看看广大网友的评价</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">如果是出国工作，而且还是小公司 那就必须超级谨慎，别怀着一个出国梦，结果出去就回不来了</p>
<figure style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0"><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/007S8ZIlly1gjubxz5sf6j315204imy6.jpg" alt="" title="" style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; display: block; margin: 0 auto; max-width: 100%"><figcaption style="line-height: inherit; margin: 10px 0 0; padding: 0; text-align: center; color: rgba(153, 153, 153, 1); font-size: 0.7em"></figcaption></figure>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">可能有些人说，这是法制社会，哪有那么恐怖，整体上来说没问题的，但是像东南亚国家 博彩业占据GDP的一大半，总不能为了你 割了自己的GDP吧。</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">擦亮眼睛，不要因为那点钱赌进去自己的未来</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">我认为，好的产品必须满足：</p>
<ul style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0 0 0 32px; list-style-type: disc">
<li style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0 0 0.5em; padding: 0"><span style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0">符合法律要求</span></li>
<li style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0 0 0.5em; padding: 0"><span style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0">符合道德约束</span></li>
<li style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0 0 0.5em; padding: 0"><span style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0">受到人们喜爱或者未来可能受到人们喜爱</span></li>
<li style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0 0 0.5em; padding: 0"><span style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0">能赚到钱的产品</span></li>
</ul>
<h3 id="h-4" style="color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.6em 0; font-weight: bold; border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(239, 112, 96, 1); font-size: 1.3em"><span style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0 3px 0 0; display: inline-block; font-weight: normal; background: rgba(239, 112, 96, 1); color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1); padding: 3px 10px 1px; border-top-right-radius: 3px; border-top-left-radius: 3px">岗位&amp;方向</span><span style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-bottom: 36px solid rgba(239, 235, 233, 1); border-right: 20px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)"> </span></h3>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">岗位和方向主要是和自己未来职业规划相匹配的</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">举个例子：</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">有人毕业做了运维，做了几年又转到业务开发，做了几年又搞了支付，做了几年又转到搜索 等等频繁更换岗位方向的。</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">经常更换岗位方向，意味着你在每个岗位都是<strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">走马观花</strong>，不可能沉淀出自己独到的见解。</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">这样你倒是尝试挺多的，满足了自己的好奇心，但是你的薪资、你的专业能力全部没有得到应有的提升，而且年龄还在增长</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">年龄红利期一过去，专业<strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">深度</strong>没有，随便找个应届生就把你踢掉，剩下的泪目生活就不必说了吧</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">选择岗位时<strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">尽量贴合</strong>自己职业规划，一般一个岗位规划3~5年时间，在这段时间里，好好研究专业方向的内容</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">好好沉淀，好好沉淀，好好沉淀  <strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">重要的事情说三遍</strong></p>
<h3 id="h-5" style="color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.6em 0; font-weight: bold; border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(239, 112, 96, 1); font-size: 1.3em"><span style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0 3px 0 0; display: inline-block; font-weight: normal; background: rgba(239, 112, 96, 1); color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1); padding: 3px 10px 1px; border-top-right-radius: 3px; border-top-left-radius: 3px">公司的发展阶段</span><span style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-bottom: 36px solid rgba(239, 235, 233, 1); border-right: 20px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)"> </span></h3>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">发展阶段主要反映公司整体<strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">技术能力</strong>和<strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">给钱能力</strong></p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">一般规律 公司起步前1~3年主要做业务量，技术架构是什么东东 不存在的，都是单体服务，也没什么并发，耦合度高的惊人。</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">能撑到第四年，说明业务模式已经经受市场检验了，这时候公司的量来了，技术架构也必须起来了，微服务、分布式、高并发设计这时候必须上了。</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">解释一下这是一般规律啊，别拿个别情况忽悠自己</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">融资情况可以看出资本对该业务的看好情况，资本看好的一个直接后果就是多金，这样你被高薪砸中的概率大。</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">资本家帮你过滤一遍，你在细细筛选一遍，基本能过滤掉一把垃圾公司。</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">当然遇上ofo，那就只能是运气不佳了…</p>
<h3 id="h-6" style="color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.6em 0; font-weight: bold; border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(239, 112, 96, 1); font-size: 1.3em"><span style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0 3px 0 0; display: inline-block; font-weight: normal; background: rgba(239, 112, 96, 1); color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1); padding: 3px 10px 1px; border-top-right-radius: 3px; border-top-left-radius: 3px">领导情况</span><span style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-bottom: 36px solid rgba(239, 235, 233, 1); border-right: 20px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)"> </span></h3>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">领导分为直属领导和创始人两个层面</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">直属领导就是你进去之后直接给你分配任务的，同时也是决定你的职业成长的。</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">遇到垃圾领导就是<strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">脏活</strong>给你干、<strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">锅给你背</strong>、升职加薪没你份。</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">更有甚者，天天给你画大饼，给你谈未来，给你谈梦想</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">遇到这种真的是大不幸，特别是刚毕业的小伙，简直会造成对世界认知的偏见</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">所以一般确定给你发offer之后，一定问HR要到直属领导或者带你学长的电话，做一个电话访谈或者微信沟通</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">访谈内容主要如下：</p>
<ul style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0 0 0 32px; list-style-type: disc">
<li style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0 0 0.5em; padding: 0"><span style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0">进去之后负责工作的具体内容是什么？</span></li>
<li style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0 0 0.5em; padding: 0"><span style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0">有没有关于你的培养计划，越详细越好？</span></li>
<li style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0 0 0.5em; padding: 0"><span style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0">组内会不会经常分享技术，频率是多少？</span></li>
<li style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0 0 0.5em; padding: 0"><span style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0">跨部门沟通多不多？</span></li>
</ul>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">说完直属领导，说说<strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">创始人</strong></p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">有人说，创始人离我很远，我工作几年也从来没见过。</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">他真的离你很远么？ 你每天都是在花自己的时间，为别人拼命的实现梦想，难道你都不知道是为谁实现么？</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">创始人非常很重要的，他不会直接和你接触，但他是谈梦想的人，你是为他实现梦想的人。</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">给你说几个创始人</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">某某创始人在年会上公然宣布996是常态化，生活工作不平衡可以离婚；某某创始人提倡四小时睡眠法，说自己坚持多年，效果良好；莫老板发全员邮件说，你们在这里工作虽然赚不了多少钱，但你们会非常的体面。</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">你说要是遇到这种创始人，你会怎样？</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">创始人情况可以网上查下，看看广大热心网友的评价怎么样</p>
<h3 id="h-7" style="color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.6em 0; font-weight: bold; border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(239, 112, 96, 1); font-size: 1.3em"><span style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0 3px 0 0; display: inline-block; font-weight: normal; background: rgba(239, 112, 96, 1); color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1); padding: 3px 10px 1px; border-top-right-radius: 3px; border-top-left-radius: 3px">薪资福利</span><span style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-bottom: 36px solid rgba(239, 235, 233, 1); border-right: 20px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)"> </span></h3>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">这块放在最后了，不是这块不重要，是相对没那么重要。</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">按照前面的条件筛选下来，基本薪资待遇八九不离十了，即使没那么高的离谱的薪资，也算是有一个明朗的未来了。</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">薪资这块一定要<strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">问清楚问具体</strong>，不要听HR忽悠，以下几个问题要特别问清楚</p>
<ol style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0 0 0 32px; list-style-type: decimal">
<li style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0 0 0.5em; padding: 0"><span style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0">薪资计算规则，一般分为以下两种：</span></li>
</ol>
<ul style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0 0 0 32px; list-style-type: disc">
<li style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0 0 0.5em; padding: 0"><span style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0">月薪*月份 + 奖金(年终奖、期权/股票、其他奖励)</span></li>
<li style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0 0 0.5em; padding: 0"><span style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0">年薪+奖金(年终奖、期权/股票、其他奖励)</span></li>
</ul>
<ol style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0 0 0 32px; list-style-type: decimal">
<li style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0 0 0.5em; padding: 0"><p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">薪资发放时间，是 **按月发放 **   <strong style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(233, 105, 0, 1)">还是按年发放</strong>   或者其他</p></li>
<li style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0 0 0.5em; padding: 0"><p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">是否有加班薪资，加班薪资怎么计算</p></li>
<li style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0 0 0.5em; padding: 0"><p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">有没有单位餐厅、是否有餐补或者房补</p></li>
<li style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0 0 0.5em; padding: 0"><p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">其他福利待遇 年假、婚假、产假等等假期</p></li>
</ol>
<h3 id="h-8" style="color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.6em 0; font-weight: bold; border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(239, 112, 96, 1); font-size: 1.3em"><span style="font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0 3px 0 0; display: inline-block; font-weight: normal; background: rgba(239, 112, 96, 1); color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1); padding: 3px 10px 1px; border-top-right-radius: 3px; border-top-left-radius: 3px">总结</span><span style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; border-bottom: 36px solid rgba(239, 235, 233, 1); border-right: 20px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)"> </span></h3>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">还是那句话，出来卖一定要卖个好价钱，和资本做谈判最好衡量的就是钱，最直接收益的也是钱。 </p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">钱多活少离家近的工作毕竟少，但可以找一个有发展潜力的、看重你的、愿意为你花钱的、合法的公司工作。</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">大家在社会中一切东西都要用白纸黑字写清楚，电话沟通能录音的尽量录音，现场也一样，做这些并不是为了其他，只是为了保护好自己。</p>
<p style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; line-height: inherit; padding: 0; margin: 1.7em 0">最后希望大家都能签一个满意的offer，我是龙叔，一个半吊子架构师，喜欢我记得关注我，给我点赞 <br>欢迎关注公众号 龙跃十二 更多精彩等着你</p></div>
</div>
